Class Patient

java.lang.Object
com.remotehealth.app.model.User
com.remotehealth.app.model.Patient
public class Patient extends User
PATIENT CLASS Represents a patient user in the system with health monitoring capabilities. Extends the base User class and adds medical-specific functionality.
